'''高溴酸钠'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为NaBrO<sub>4</sub>。它可由[[溴酸钠|溴酸钠]]和[[氟气|氟气]]在碱性条件中反应得到。<ref>Barkov, S. Production of perbromic acid and perbromates. ''Khimiya v Shkole'', 1971. 3: 18. ISSN: 0368-5632.</ref>[[高溴酸|高溴酸]]和[[氢氧化钠|氢氧化钠]]的中和反应也能制备高溴酸钠。<ref>{{cite book|author=Kurt H. Stern|title=High Temperature Properties and Thermal Decomposition of Inorganic Salts with Oxyanions|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=R4PLBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA224|date=2000-09-21|publisher=CRC Press|isbn=978-1-4200-4234-4|pages=224}}</ref>它可以形成[[单斜晶系|单斜晶系]]的一水合物。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Acta Crystallographica Section C Crystal Structure Communications|volume=48|issue=3|date=1992-03-15|pages=419–424|doi=10.1107/S0108270191010818|url=http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0108270191010818|title=Structure of sodium perbromate monohydrate|accessdate=2021-01-25|author=A. C. Blackburn, J. C. Gallucci, R. E. Gerkin, W. J. Reppart|archive-date=2018-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180603110427/http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0108270191010818|dead-url=no}}</ref>

